item.title: Typing Terror - Yet Another!
item.dc:creator: @aznph8playa aznph8playa
item.description:
@aznph8playa wrote:

Not much to comment on… it’s the same old script from before and the play button selection doesnt work.
For future reference, don’t use bitmaps of such large size, they’ll just slow down the program. You can use small bitmaps and be assured that there aren’t too many instances where you’ll have the program confuse what you’re looking for. Try 2x10s insteads of 80 x11s.
